<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Управление спортивным инвентарем</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #2c3e50;
            --accent-color: #e74c3c;
        }

        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.9), rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.9)),
            url('https://source.unsplash.com/random/1920x1080/?sports-equipment') center/cover;
            height: 104vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
        }

        .feature-card {
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 15px;
            background-color: #c4ced8;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        #features h1,
        #features h3 {
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        #features .card-body i {
            color: #344a60 !important;
        }
        .nav-pills {
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .scrollspy-section {
            padding: 100px 0;
        }

        .partner-logo {
            filter: grayscale(100%);
            transition: filter 0.3s;
            max-height: 50px;
        }

        .partner-logo:hover {
            filter: grayscale(0);
        }

        .cta-button {
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        

        .hero-image {
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body data-bs-spy="scroll" data-bs-target="#mainNav">
<nav id="mainNav" class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark fixed-top">
    <div class="container">
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
            <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="btn btn-outline-light ms-2" href="/Account/Login">Регистрация</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="btn btn-outline-light ms-2" href="/Account/Login">Войти</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero-section">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Г А Н Т Е Л Ь К А</h1>
                <p class="lead mb-4">Управляйте спортивным инвентарем, как супергерой!</p>
                <a href="/Account/Login" class="btn btn-lg btn-outline-light me-3 cta-button">Начать сейчас</a>
                <a href="#features" class="btn btn-lg btn-outline-light cta-button">Узнать больше</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 d-none d-lg-block">
                <img src="/images/menuPhoto.jpg" alt="Инвентарь" class="img-fluid hero-image">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="features" class="scrollspy-section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="text-center mb-5">Хочешь заниматься спортом и тебе нужен инвентарь?</h1>
        <h3 class="text-center mb-5">Выбирай и резервируй спортивный инвентарь у нас!!!</h3>
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card feature-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <i class="fa fa-bicycle fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                        <h5 class="card-title">Предоставим спортивный инвентарь в соответствии с заказом</h5>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card feature-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-clipboard-list fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                        <h5 class="card-title">А если нет в наличии, сформируем заявки на новое оборудование</h5>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card feature-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <i class="fa fa-envelope-open fa-3x text-primary mb-3" ></i>
                        <h5 class="card-title">Сломались лыжи, коньки - обеспечим замену и ремонт</h5>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
<script>
    
    window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
        const statsSection = document.getElementById('stats');
        const position = statsSection.getBoundingClientRect();
        if(position.top < window.innerHeight) {
            animateCounters();
            window.removeEventListener('scroll', this);
        }
    });
    
    document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
        anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
            e.preventDefault();
            document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({
                behavior: 'smooth'
            });
        });
    });
</script>
</body>
</html>